comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T06:58:06.206Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: total closed=798, generator item_count=782, delta=16 = exactly the pm-iqgj-recovered files (pm-3akm/ss8d/1r6p... none present in CHANGELOG.pm.md while normal closed items pm-qsk8/c98b/xh0y/dpzc are). Extension dir has node_modules/@unbrained/pm-cli (bundled). Root-cause fix shipped in this PR via pm-iqgj (src/core/item/toon-decode.ts + parseToonItemDocument); this issue tracks propagation/hardening only and is blocked_by pm-iqgj."
  "2026-05-24T07:02:51.595Z",claude-code-agent,Submitted in PR #58 (branch recover-unreadable-toon-items-and-dedup-core-helpers).
